5: I was banned from the venue.
10:
He truly was too good at his job... We
were suspected of using a cryptic
artifact and driven out.
14:
Hahahaha. They were not entirely
incorrect.
17:
However, to compare a sacred relic
like myself with that level of magical
object is an insult to all my partners,
past and present—
21:
*sigh* If only Finn were willing to be
more flexible.
25:
So here we are. My partner, we turn
to you for aid.
39:
I can't be working every day.
Naturally, the position then falls to
you, Alk.
44:
W-wait, hold on. You can't seriously
expect me to do this, right? There's
no way I can—
49:
You turn your eyes from the truth.
Every soul in this town recognizes
your brilliance for what it is.
53:
Besides, it's not up to you to decide
how others feel about you. Am I
wrong?
62:
I assume this means you have not
heard the masses clamoring for you
to become a prince at the venue.
67:
You'll be fine. Act freely, following
your whims like you always do, and
that will be enough.
72:
Hey! I didn't say I'd do it! Are you
listening to me?!
82:
Dear, oh dear. The customers
appear to be happy, but...
85:
Is this all according to your plan,
Diviner?
89:
Is this not what you wanted? It's our
turn now.
93: Relax, Alk. You have our assistance.
112:
I-I do! I'll take anything that'll get me
out of this suffering!
115: Then use me to your heart's content.
118:
For Ame no Murakumo—blade and
spirit—shall cut through any
obstacle!
124: True Prince Alk, at your service!
131: Sorry for keeping you all waiting.
134:
Thank you for coming today. I'm
overjoyed to be surrounded by so
many lovely princesses today...
137:
Oh, no... What's wrong, Alk? Did
something happen to you?
140:
I want to make you all happy—to the
best of my ability to do so.
149:
What is this?! What's happening to
me? Huh?!
153:
Hahahaha. Calm yourself, my
partner. You required my strength,
and this is the result.
156:
Leave everything to me. I shall draw
out the hidden potential sleeping
within you!
163:
Heya, Alk! We came to see how
you're doing!
168:
S-Sohvi, I'm not very comfortable
entering this kind of place...
173: We're here to crash the party.
186:
All of you look positively ravishing
today. But you will have to forgive
me, for I—
236:
Hard to believe that's sincere, after
you just laughed in my face!
238:
I can't believe you did that! In front
of those two of all people!
244:
No, truly, I apologize. I simply... felt
the urge to act that way and
followed that urge.
247:
This is the first time I have gone
against the wishes of a partner of
mine. I have failed my duty as a
blade.
251:
Honestly, it's probably best if you
keep that up.
254:
Well, I'd rather you never took
control of me and said those things
again.
256:
But otherwise, I'm happy when you
don't treat yourself as a tool.
263:
But say what you will—I am a blade.
It is in my nature to help you fulfill
your dreams.
269:
But just... I'm not comfortable with
that flirty stuff, okay? At least, not
now!
275:
It seems that I will have to mark this
job as a failure, then.
